for *k*arati it is said here *k*aret).

<span id="fn_811"></span>[318:2](sbe29181.htm#fr_812.md) *S*atapatha
Brâhma*n*a l.l. § 30.

<span id="fn_812"></span>[318:3](sbe29181.htm#fr_813.md) *S*atapatha
Brâhma*n*a l.l. § 31. Black birds, according to the commentators, mean
crows.

<span id="fn_813"></span>[318:4](sbe29181.htm#fr_814.md) Funeral food is
such food as described below, III, 10, 26.

<span id="fn_814"></span>[319:9](sbe29181.htm#fr_815.md) The Pravargya
ceremony, one of the preparatory ceremonies of the Soma sacrifice
